144
00:07:21,003 --> 00:07:24,760
And it's a diverse and multidimensional
subject.

145
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:27,448
It's also a powerful way of expressing
relationships and

146
00:07:27,448 --> 00:07:32,540
ideas in numerical, pictorial, graphical,
verbal and symbolic forms.

147
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:35,620
So let's together introduce students to
that world of exciting and

148
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:37,210
beautiful maths.

149
00:07:37,210 --> 00:07:40,020
